sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant ContactUI as Home Contact Form
    participant MsgAPI as POST /api/messages
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant MailService as Mail Service (Nodemailer)
    participant GmailSMTP as Gmail SMTP
    participant Inbox as Admin Inbox (hello@mance.dev)

    Visitor->>ContactUI: Submit contact form
    ContactUI->>MsgAPI: Send name, email, subject, message
    MsgAPI->>DB: Persist MESSAGE row
    DB-->>MsgAPI: Message created

    par Notify admin
        MsgAPI->>MailService: Compose admin notification
        MailService->>GmailSMTP: sendMail(admin template)
        GmailSMTP-->>MailService: 250 accepted
        MailService-->>MsgAPI: Delivery result + messageId
        MsgAPI-->>Inbox: New inquiry email delivered
    and Send visitor acknowledgment
        MsgAPI->>MailService: Compose visitor acknowledgment
        MailService->>GmailSMTP: sendMail(visitor receipt)
        GmailSMTP-->>MailService: 250 accepted
        MailService-->>MsgAPI: Delivery result + messageId
    end

    MsgAPI-->>ContactUI: 201 Created + success state
    ContactUI-->>Visitor: Confirmation message shown
